wikipedia_page.main: Stephanie Mary Proud (born 29 August 1988) is an English competitive swimmer who has represented Great Britain at the Olympics, and England in the Commonwealth Games.As a member of the British team at the 2012 Summer Olympics in London, Proud competed in the women's 200-metre backstroke event.  She advanced to the 200-metre event semifinals, and came ninth overall, with a time of 2:09.04.
